    "attributes": {
        "action": "Cancel the GCSE exams for summer 2023",
        "additional_details": "The ongoing COVID-19 pandemic is a strong reason to cancel GCSE exams for 2023. The pandemic has already caused significant disruptions to the education system for multiple years, including school closures, remote learning, and interruptions to regular exams.\r\n\r\nBy cancelling the exams in 2023, schools could have more flexibility to provide high-quality education to students under challenging circumstances, without the added pressure of preparing for exams.",
        "background": "I want the Government to cancel the GCSE exams.",
